{"tid":1939194,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"太一同亞古獸返去現代哩段算唔算係全系列最精妙嘅劇情","createTime":"2020-03-23T04:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T07:20:35.000Z","uid":141869,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"64d3b21a83da97d28a70cf81cd2ae9e4219226d2","tid":1939194,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"哩集作為兩個章節之間嘅過渡，係信息量同劇情推進上都係無與倫比嘅，<br />\n1.帶出兩個世界時間流動速度唔同，合理化佢地冒險左咁耐但現實冇人知<br />\n2.為吸血魔獸來到現實世界做伏線<br />\n3.帶出第八個被選中嘅細路小光<br />\n4.得亞古獸可以進化成完全體嘅情況下，認為自己有必要返去數碼世界，展示出太一嘅責任心<br />\n5.太一離開左其他人就各散東西，確立太一領導地位<br />\n6.<del><span style=\"color: red;\">展示太一同小光超越兄妹嘅感情</span></del>（官方澄清左冇哩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n以一套兒童向動畫黎講，喺每集都打一隻怪為主調嘅情況下，哩集真係好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef44b0d3c1e524a69fa30cf3a24b521945dd98a","tid":1939194,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"大門大獸"},{"pid":"fa1ece266bfeaa6db3ba927f641cb2ea15333188","tid":1939194,"uid":214806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"識睇一定係睇第 21 集<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142ece12d6b131dba14ea702b809396054aa091c","tid":1939194,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"唔錯"},{"pid":"953d4d3abdd9c27a20ba4cd83fbd912857818348","tid":1939194,"uid":90282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"細個睇呢集同滾球獸誕生好似，無論畫風，節奏，bgm都係<br />\n<br />\n唔記得左點解太一失蹤後成隊人散哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"95a607b303729dfb11cc4dcbd5d071a03b2e0782","tid":1939194,"uid":13151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"妹控<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /