，應該係全貴最好睇嘅幾集之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜爛尾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"第二季邊集，<br />\n講類似我覺得第四季托也回到過去阻止自己去數碼世界嗰集都唔差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"13集 達高獸的呼喚<br />\n講小光入咗個黑暗版數碼世界，然後阿岳去救<br />\n我覺得呢個世界好值得拓展，點知最後淨係用黎sd 個boss 入去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1025fb98d90ac32a286d01082e44d01592b81d00","tid":1939194,"uid":277031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2bdbb99982fd8e2d9616e061bcb92d77f5adb30","tid":1939194,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"第5可唔可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"太一翻去之後成個team 散曬<br />\n之後太一翻到黎逐個逐個搵翻佢地，先團結到去打吸血魔獸"},{"pid":"4406919aa2b4618ef7144dd359e9668d05ce1d33","tid":1939194,"uid":151488,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"數碼世界俾吸血魔獸追殺緊, 城堡入面太一揀卡開門返現實世界果集好刺激"},{"pid":"bb8c391c2577f8c8be963067b1e800d5f831ad1e","tid":1939194,"uid":102880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9bc23c9b87e4144727836bf3f64cfe741ea5886b","tid":1939194,"uid":141869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"953d4d3abdd9c27a20ba4cd83fbd912857818348","tid":1939194,"uid":90282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"細個睇呢集同滾球獸誕生好似，無論畫風，節奏，bgm都係<br />\n<br />\n唔記得左點解太一失蹤後成隊人散哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"劇場版嗰種手繪畫風真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:42:29.000Z","msg":"細田守風格, 唔知點解我覺得咁先係數碼暴龍既真正應有風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識形容, 好似有種孤獨既feel, 但係又唔完全係, 唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024d1cf60aa688797faccf617